	(2,1,'2017-12-12 06:25:17','2017-12-12 06:25:17','Based on the professionally social network with the advantage of quickly updating new trends, the habit of sharing experiences, exchanging and discussing within our community as well as the need to develop skills and expertise, we have developed a series of <strong>Hospitality Talk</strong> and supposed it as one of the key activities of the program <em>\"Developing the high quality human resource system for Vietnam’s Tourism and Hospitality for the period 2015 - 2020\".</em>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-50 \" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1587619385666836900-talk1d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"769\" height=\"432\" />\r\n\r\nHospitality Talk will be held monthly with various themes which are selected from all sectors in the industry. Joining the online event, users have the opportunities to discuss directly with experts and special guests who are working for national or international corporations as well as meet and share experiences with the community who has the same concern.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-48 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/979173431324870647-12961466101540173161766353026370230780444211n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"763\" height=\"499\" /> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-49 \" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1522266628310492830-12472457101540173148916351812097324804453541n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"761\" height=\"507\" />\r\n\r\nWe expect Hospitality Talk will bring value to the community of Tourism and Hospitality, directly contribute to improve the quality of human resources.','Online Panel','','publish','closed','open','','online-panel','','','2017-12-14 12:22:24','2017-12-14 12:22:24','',0,'http://localhost:81/wordpress/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),
