	(88,1,'2017-12-14 12:48:41','2017-12-14 12:48:41','<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-89 size-large\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/999994574611508522-hcflogobeta-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"780\" height=\"780\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>PRESS RELEASE</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>HOSPITALITY CAREER FAIR 2015</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>Sponsorship</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Department of Tourism of Ho Chi Minh City</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>Organizing Committee</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Vietnam Hospitality Network</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Ton Duc Thang University</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>Media Sponsorship</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Ho Chi Minh City Television (HTV)</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Vietnam Television (VTV24)</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Travel and Entertainment Magazine</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">Hoteliers.vn</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\">***</p>\r\nOn December 19, 2015, <strong>Hospitality Career Fair (HCF 2015)</strong> will be held in Ho Chi Minh city for the first time, continuing the success of ‘<em>’Vietnam Hoteliers – Developing the high quality human resources system in Vietnam Tourism and Hospitality in the period 2015 - 2020’’</em> and “<em>Young Hotelier Award 2015</em>”. HFC 2015 will be taken place in the sporting event hall of Ton Duc Thang University, 19 Nguyen Huu Tho, District 7, Ho Chi Minh city with the participation of the Organizing Committee, Sponsorship, Media Sponsor, representatives from enterprises, experts, lecturers, and students majored in Tourism and Hospitality.\r\n\r\nHFC 2015 attracts more than 5000 personnel working in this sector with more than 40 enterprises with these following activities:\r\n\r\n- Career Opportunities booths with the participation of famous groups, hotels, tourism companies, and restaurant chains in Vietnam. In HFC, students will have the chance to meet recruiters, be interviewed and apply for suitable jobs.\r\n\r\n- Specialized workshop leaded by experts who are senior managers in Tourism and Hospitality.\r\n\r\n- Interview Opportunity for Scholarship of Hospitality One-Stop Development from VHN and other enterprises.\r\n\r\nWith the aim to connect and create 500 career opportunities with more than 20 scholarships, HFC 2015 hopes to become a place for Schools, Enterprises, Experts, and Young Talents in Tourism and Hospitality to meet and share development opportunities in this sector. HFC 2015 also expects to become a typical and annual event  for Vietnam Tourism and Hospitality.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>For more information, please contact:</strong></em>\r\n\r\nMs. Sally Bui (Head of Organizing Commitee)\r\n\r\nTel: 093 453 9067\r\n\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:careerfair@hospitality.vn\">careerfair@hospitality.vn</a> / <a href=\"mailto:sally.bui@hospitality.vn\">sally.bui@hospitality.vn</a>','Hospitality Career Fair 2015','','publish','open','open','','hospitality-career-fair-2015','','','2017-12-14 13:02:17','2017-12-14 13:02:17','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=88',0,'post','',0),
